  "description": "A storage program that allows the user to place up to 1500 Pokémon collected from the various Game Boy Advance installments of the franchise onto one Memory Card.  The game is compatible with <i>Pokémon</i> <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=Pok%c3%a9mon+Ruby\">Ruby</a>, <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=Pok%c3%a9mon+Sapphire\">Sapphire</a>, <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=Pok%c3%a9mon+Emerald\">Emerald</a>, and <i>Pokémon</i> <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=Pok%c3%a9mon+FireRed\">FireRed</a> &amp; <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=Pok%c3%a9mon+LeafGreen\">LeafGreen</a>.  It allows users to play <i>Pokémon Ruby</i> &amp; <i>Sapphire</i> on their GameCube without a Game Boy Advance player, but a <i>Ruby</i> or <i>Sapphire</i> cart is required.  The set also includes a Game Boy Advance link cable and a GameCube memory card.",
